> To compile
	$ make

> To install the driver
	$ make install
	* It is important to verify if there is another driver and remove it
		$ make unistall_others

> To uninstall the driver
	$ make uninstall

> Manual installation
	# insmod arduino_mearm.ko

> Manual uninstall
	# rmmod arduino_mearm.ko